TITLE: Defining Translatable Texts in i18n.properties
DESCRIPTION: This snippet defines the key-value pairs for translatable texts in the `i18n.properties` file.  `showHelloButtonText` is used for the button label and `helloMsg` contains a placeholder `{0}` which will be replaced with the recipient's name at runtime. This file serves as the central repository for texts, allowing for easy translation into different languages.
SOURCE: https://github.com/sap/openui5-docs/blob/main/docs/03_Get-Started/step-8-translatable-texts-df86bfb.md#_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: properties
CODE:
```
showHelloButtonText=Say Hello
helloMsg=Hello {0}
```

