TITLE: Defining Library Dependencies in Manifest.json (JSON)
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to define library dependencies within the manifest.json file of an OpenUI5 application.  It ensures that only the specified libraries are loaded, preventing unnecessary resource consumption. The 'minUI5Version' specifies the minimum OpenUI5 version required.
SOURCE: https://github.com/sap/openui5-docs/blob/main/docs/03_Get-Started/load-only-what-you-really-need-e8fca3e.md#_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: JSON
CODE:
```
"sap.ui5": {
	"dependencies": {
		"minUI5Version": "1.60.0",
		"libs": {
			"sap.ui.core": {},
			"sap.m": {},
			"sap.ui.layout": {}
		}
	}
	...
}
```

