TITLE: Simple Data Binding in XML View - OpenUI5
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates simple data binding in an OpenUI5 XML view.  It binds the `value` property of an `Input` control to the `/firstName` property of a data model. This enables the Input field to display the value stored in the model's `firstName` property.
SOURCE: https://github.com/sap/openui5-docs/blob/main/docs/04_Essentials/binding-syntax-e2e6f41.md#_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: xml
CODE:
```
<Input value="{/firstName}"/>
```

