TITLE: Configuring Data Source URI for Local Proxy in manifest.json - JSON
DESCRIPTION: This code shows how to modify the `uri` in the `manifest.json` file to point to the local proxy server. By prefixing the remote service URL with the proxy's address, requests are routed through the proxy, bypassing the same-origin policy restriction during local development. You must have a local proxy server already configured to use this.
