LANGUAGE: JSON
CODE:
```
{
	"sap.app": {
		...
		"dataSources": {
			"northwind": {
				"uri": "http://localhost:8081/https://services.odata.org/V2/Northwind/Northwind.svc/",

				"type": "OData",
				"settings": {
					"odataVersion": "2.0"
				}
			}
		}
	}
}
