TITLE: Implementing Aggregation Binding in App.view.xml (XML)
DESCRIPTION: This XML snippet defines a panel containing an `sap.m.List` control. The `items` aggregation of the list is bound to the `products>/Products` path, which refers to the `Products` array in the `products` model.  An `sap.m.ObjectListItem` is used as a template, and it is cloned for each product in the model.
