TITLE: Open Dialog in Controller (TypeScript)
DESCRIPTION: This TypeScript code defines an event handler `onOpenDialog` in the `HelloPanel` controller. It asynchronously loads the `HelloDialog` fragment, stores it as a property of the controller instance, and opens the dialog when triggered. It leverages `async/await` for asynchronous handling.
