TITLE: Configuring Routing in manifest.json (JSON)
DESCRIPTION: This snippet configures routing in the `manifest.json` file. It defines routes and targets for navigation between the overview and detail pages.  The `config` section defines the router class and default view settings. The `routes` section defines URL patterns and their corresponding targets. The `targets` section defines the views to be displayed for each target.
