TITLE: Attaching to `RouteMatched` event in OpenUI5 (JavaScript)
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet demonstrates how to attach to the `RouteMatched` event of a specific route using OpenUI5's routing API. The code gets the Router instance, retrieves a route, and attaches a handler function to the `matched` event. The handler extracts an ID from the event parameters.
