TITLE: Component Container Configuration - JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: This JavaScript code demonstrates how to programmatically create and configure a `ComponentContainer` within a custom bootstrap module.  It defines the component name, manifest settings, lifecycle, and event handlers for `componentCreated` and `componentFailed`. The component container is then placed into the DOM using `placeAt("content")`.
