LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
{
			...
			"routes": [
				{
					"pattern": ":layout:",
					"name": "list",
					"target": [
						"list",
						"detail"
					]
				},
				{
					"pattern": "detail/{product}/{layout}",
					"name": "detail",
					"target": [
						"list",
						"detail"
					]
