TITLE: Simple Unit Formatting with CLDR - JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates basic unit formatting and parsing using CLDR data. It initializes a unit format instance and formats a number with 'speed-mile-per-hour' unit, and parses a string back into number and unit. Requires sap/ui/core/format/NumberFormat.
