TITLE: Setting Header Context for $count Property Binding in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: This JavaScript code snippet shows how to set the header context for a property binding to `$count`. It retrieves the `ODataListBinding` for the `SalesOrders` table and then sets the binding context of the `SalesOrdersTitle` control to the header context of the list binding.
SOURCE: https://github.com/sap/openui5-docs/blob/main/docs/04_Essentials/binding-collection-inline-count-77d2310.md#_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: JavaScript
CODE:
```
