TITLE: Using Component.getOwnerComponentFor - JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: This code demonstrates how to retrieve the owner component for a `ManagedObject` (e.g., a `sap.m.Page` control) using the static `Component.getOwnerComponentFor` function.  After obtaining the owner component, the `runAsOwner` method is called to create additional `ManagedObject`s within the correct owner component scope. This is useful when creating controls outside of a controller instance.
SOURCE: https://github.com/sap/openui5-docs/blob/main/docs/04_Essentials/the-owner-component-a7a3138.md#_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: JavaScript
