TITLE: Setting Currency Model in Detail Controller - TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: This TypeScript code initializes a JSON model with currency information in the `Detail` controller. It creates a new `JSONModel` instance with a `currency` property set to "EUR". This model is then set on the view with the name "view", enabling data binding to display currency information within the view.
SOURCE: https://github.com/sap/openui5-docs/blob/main/docs/03_Get-Started/step-35-device-adaptation-typescript-ab8ed1b.md#_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: TypeScript
