TITLE: Using InvisibleMessage with MessageStrip - JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: This code demonstrates how to use the `sap.ui.core.InvisibleMessage` class to announce a dynamically generated `sap.m.MessageStrip` to screen readers. It initializes the InvisibleMessage instance, creates a MessageStrip with specific properties, and uses the announce method to inform the user about the message.
