TITLE: Attaching parse error handler to component in SAPUI5
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to attach a parse error handler to a component in SAPUI5, using `Component.create()` and `attachParseError()`. It also shows how to detach the handler. Requires `sap/ui/core/Component` module.
