TITLE: Creating a Dialog using JS Fragment in OpenUI5
DESCRIPTION: This JavaScript fragment defines a dialog containing an input field and a close button. The fragment's `createContent` function instantiates the dialog and its content, binding the input field's text to the '/dialogText' model property. The close button's press event closes the dialog. Requires `sap/m/Dialog`, `sap/m/Input`, and `sap/m/Button` modules.
