TITLE: Configuring UI5 Tooling (ui5.yaml)
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet configures the UI5 Tooling setup by specifying the OpenUI5 framework and version, along with libraries dependencies and custom tasks. It defines custom middleware for transpiling modern JavaScript, serving the OpenUI5 framework, and enabling live reload. The configuration ensures that TypeScript is transpiled and that the development environment is optimized with live reload functionality.
