TITLE: Initializing Router in Component.ts (TypeScript)
DESCRIPTION: This snippet initializes the router in the component's `init` method.  It calls `this.getRouter().initialize()` to start the routing process. This will evaluate the current URL and load the corresponding view based on the routes defined in the `manifest.json` file.
