TITLE: Configuring Routing with Title Propagation in OpenUI5 (JSON)
DESCRIPTION: This JSON snippet demonstrates how to configure routing in an OpenUI5 application to propagate the 'titleChanged' event from a nested component to the parent component. The 'propagateTitle' property is set to true in the target configuration.
