TITLE: Activating Table Personalization with Unified Shell - JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: This JavaScript code snippet demonstrates how to instantiate and activate a table personalization controller using the Unified Shell's Personalization service. It retrieves a personalization service provider from the shell, creates a table personalization controller instance connected to a table and persistence service, activates the controller, and attaches a press event to a button to open the dialog.
