TITLE: OData V4 Binding with Group ID in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: This JavaScript code snippet demonstrates how to create an OData V4 model and bind a context and property with a specified update group ID. The `$$updateGroupId` parameter is used to assign the group ID 'myGroup' to the update requests for the binding, allowing batching of updates.
