TITLE: Defining Code List Annotations for Currency and Units in OData Metadata (XML)
DESCRIPTION: This XML snippet demonstrates how to define code list annotations for currency codes and units of measure in an OData metadata document. It specifies the annotations `com.sap.vocabularies.CodeList.v1.CurrencyCodes` and `com.sap.vocabularies.CodeList.v1.UnitsOfMeasure` pointing to the respective code list services and their collection paths. It also showcases the use of `Org.OData.Measures.V1.ISOCurrency` and `Org.OData.Measures.V1.Unit` to associate properties with currency codes and units.
