DESCRIPTION: This JavaScript code demonstrates how to load a fragment using the `loadFragment` method available on controller instances in OpenUI5. This method automatically prefixes the fragment's content IDs with the view ID, preventing ID collisions. The fragment `my.useful.UiPartZ` is loaded asynchronously.
