TITLE: Replacing sap.ui.jsview and showing View.extend with View.create - JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: This section explains how to replace the `sap.ui.jsview` factory and shows the recommended approach of extending `sap.ui.core.mvc.View` using `View.extend` for defining views.  It also demonstrates how to use `View.create` to load and create a view instance. The example uses `sap.ui.define` to define a new View class that extends `sap.ui.core.mvc.View`. It also shows how to load and instantiate this typed view.
SOURCE: https://github.com/sap/openui5-docs/blob/main/docs/04_Essentials/deprecated-factories-replacement-491bd9c.md#_snippet_7

LANGUAGE: JavaScript
CODE:
```
