LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
const libraryName = "lib";
sap.ui.define([
    "sap/ui/core/Lib"
], (Library) => {
    "use strict";
    const thisLib = Library.init({{
         name: "my." + libraryName
    }});
});
```

