TITLE: Replacing initLibrary with Lib.init() in UI5 JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows the replacement of the deprecated `sap.ui.getCore().initLibrary()` with `Library.init()` for initializing a library in SAP UI5. The `init` function takes a configuration object with details about the library.
