LANGUAGE: JavaScript
CODE:
```
// the object is no longer passed into sap.ui.getCore().initLibrary()
sap.ui.require(["sap/ui/core/Lib"], (Library) => {
    Library.init({
        name: "my.library",
        version: "${version}",
        dependencies: ["sap.ui.core", "..."],
        types: [
            ...
        ],
        interfaces: [],
        controls: [
            ...
        ],
        elements: [
            ...
        ],
        extensions: {
            ...
        }
    });
});
```

